metadata.description:
'Back Home' is a tale about a musician's life on the road touring, chasing a dream while missing the people they love the most and leave behind while on their musical journey.

Dre from 'The Gooneez' says this about the lyrics, "At the time we were writing this song, me and my cousin Frank had been gone doing a lot of shows on tour but were missing our family & friends that we were both needed some sense of normalcy again to our soul that only home can bring."

The song also features a live band production from The Gooneez own backline that brings a true feel to the sound of the track.

'Back Home' is the second drop on sound xyz from the Southern California alternative hip-hop group.
